      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/logistics-firm-wwex-group-taps-underwriters-for-potential-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，第三方物流供应商WWEX集团在可能进行美国首次公开募股之前已选定承销商。]]></description>
