    <item>
      <title>DEA 将重新分类大麻的报告导致大麻库存飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pot-stocks-surge-on-report-dea-is-moving-to-reclassify-marijuana</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国缉毒局将大麻重新归类为危险性较低的药物类别后，大麻相关公司的股价周二大幅上涨，这对该行业来说将是一个历史性的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pot-stocks-surge-on-report-dea-is-moving-to-reclassify-marijuana</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:45:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于投资者“无处可去”，沃尔格林股价遭受重创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/walgreens-wba-stock-lashed-as-investors-left-with-nothing-to-go-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔格林联合博姿公司 (Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc.) 股价本月遭遇五年多来最差表现，这家陷入困境的连锁药店正经历艰难的转型，导致投资者纷纷抛售该股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/walgreens-wba-stock-lashed-as-investors-left-with-nothing-to-go-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 16:23:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗戈夫称市场将抵制美联储面临的任何政治压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/rogoff-says-markets-would-upend-political-bashing-of-the-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学经济学教授肯尼思·罗格夫表示，金融市场将有效限制美国总统迫使美联储放松货币政策的任何举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/rogoff-says-markets-would-upend-political-bashing-of-the-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街因美联储紧张情绪而关闭四月：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心顽固的通胀将迫使美联储在更长时间内维持较高利率，股市在四月最后一段时间下跌，债券收益率攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
